                 тФВ\n38: тФВ  тФМтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФР тФВ\n39: тФВ  тФВ                     Gin HTTP Engine                                 тФВ тФВ\n40: тФВ  тФВ  тФМтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФР  тФМтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФР  тФМтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФР  тФМтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФР тФВ тФВ\n41: тФВ  тФВ  тФВ   Auth      тФВ  тФВ   Execute   тФВ  тФВ   Files     тФВ  тФВ  Health  тФВ тФВ тФВ\n42: тФВ  тФВ  тФВ  Middleware тФВ  тФВ   Handler   тФВ  тФВ   Handler   тФВ  тФВ  Check   тФВ тФВ тФВ\n43: тФВ  тФВ  тФФтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФШ  тФФтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФШ  тФФтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФШ  тФФтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФШ тФВ тФВ\n44: тФВ  тФФтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФШ тФВ\n45: тФВ                                    тФВ                                      тФВ\n46: тФВ  тФМтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФР тФВ\n47: тФВ  тФВ                    AuthManager                                        тФВ тФВ\n48: тФВ  тФВ  тФМтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФР  тФМтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФР                                    тФВ тФВ\n49: тФВ  тФВ  тФВ  Public Key тФВ  тФВ   JWT       тФВ                                    тФВ тФВ\n50: тФВ  тФВ  тФВ  Loading    тФВ  тФВ  Validation тФВ                                    тФВ тФВ\n51: тФВ  тФВ  тФФтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФШ  тФФтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФШ                                    тФВ тФВ\n52: тФВ  тФФтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФШ тФВ\n53: тФВ                                    тФВ                                      тФВ\n54: тФВ  тФМтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФР тФВ\n55: тФВ  тФВ                   Workspace Manager                                  тФВ тФВ\n56: тФВ  тФВ  тФМтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФР  тФМтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФР                                    тФВ тФВ\n57: тФВ  тФВ  тФВ   Path      тФВ  тФВ    File     тФВ                                    тФВ тФВ\n58: тФВ  тФВ  тФВ  Sanitize   тФВ  тФВ   OperationsтФВ                                    тФВ тФВ\n59: тФВ  тФВ  тФФтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФШ  тФФтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФШ                                    тФВ тФВ\n60: тФВ  тФФтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФШ тФВ\n61: тФФтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФШ\n62: ```\n63: \n64: ### 2.2 ч╗Дф╗╢шБМш┤г\n65: \n66: | ч╗Дф╗╢ | шБМш┤г |\n67: |------|------|\n68: | `Server` | HTTP цЬНхКбф╕╗хЕехПгя╝МчобчРЖ Gin х╝ХцУОхТМщЕНч╜о |\n69: | `AuthManager` | JWT шодшпБхЕмщТехКаш╜╜хТМ Token щкМшпБ |\n70: | `ExecuteHandler` | хдДчРЖхС╜ф╗дцЙзшбМшп╖ц▒Вя╝Мш┐ФхЫЮ stdout/stderr/exit code |\n71: | `UploadFileHandler` | хдДчРЖцЦЗф╗╢ф╕Кф╝ая╝ИJSON Base64 цИЦ Multipartя╝Й |\n72: | `ListFilesHandler` | хИЧхЗ║чЫох╜ХцЦЗф╗╢ |\n73: | `DownloadFileHandler` | цЦЗф╗╢ф╕Лш╜╜ |\n74: | `HealthCheckHandler` | хБех║╖цгАцЯецОехПг |\n75: | `sanitizePath` | ш╖пх╛ДхоЙхЕицгАцЯея╝МщШ▓цнвчЫох╜Хчй┐ш╢К |\n76: \n77: ### 2.3 цХ░цНоц╡Б\n78: \n79: ```\n80: 1. ховцИ╖члпшп╖ц▒В тЖТ HTTP Server\n81:    тФВ\n82: 2. Auth Middleware щкМшпБ JWT\n83:    тФЬтФАтФА Token цЬЙцХИ тЖТ ч╗зч╗нхдДчРЖ\n84:    тФЬтФАтФА Token цЧацХИ тЖТ 401 Unauthorized\n85:    тФВ\n86: 3. шп╖ц▒Вш╖пчФ▒хИ░хЕ╖ф╜У Handler\n87:    тФЬтФАтФА /api/execute тЖТ ExecuteHandler\n88:    тФЬтФАтФА /api/files (POST) тЖТ UploadFileHandler\n89:    тФЬтФАтФА /api/files (GET) тЖТ ListFilesHandler\n90:    тФЬтФАтФА /api/files/*path тЖТ DownloadFileHandler\n91:    тФВ\n92: 4. Workspace ш╖пх╛ДщкМшпБ (sanitizePath)\n93:    тФЬтФАтФА ш╖пх╛ДхоЙхЕи тЖТ цЙзшбМцУНф╜Ь\n94:    тФЬтФАтФА ш╖пх╛Дф╕НхоЙхЕи тЖТ 403 Forbidden\n95:    тФВ\n96: 5. ш┐ФхЫЮхУНх║Ф\n97: ```\n98: \n99: ---\n100: \n101: ## 3. цХ░цНоч╗УцЮД\n102: \n103: ### 3.1 щЕНч╜оч╗УцЮД\n104: \n105: ```go\n106: type Config struct {\n107:     Port      int    `json:\"port\"`\n108:     Workspace string `json:\"workspace\"`\n109: }\n110: ```\n111: \n112: ### 3.2 Server ч╗УцЮД\n113: \n114: ```go\n115: type Server struct {\n116:     engine       *gin.Engine\n117:     config       Config\n118:     authManager  *AuthManager\n119:     startTime    time.Time\n120:     workspaceDir string\n121: }\n122: ```\n123: \n124: ### 3.3 шодшпБчобчРЖхЩи\n125: \n126: ```go\n127: type AuthManager struct {\n128:     publicKey *rsa.PublicKey\n129:     mutex     sync.RWMutex\n130: }\n131: ```\n132: \n133: ### 3.4 шп╖ц▒В/хУНх║Фч╗УцЮД\n134: \n135: #### Execute\n136: \n137: ```go\n138: type ExecuteRequest struct {\n139:     Command    []string          `json:\"command\" binding:\"required\"`\n140:     Timeout    string            `json:\"timeout\"`\n141:     WorkingDir string            `json:\"working_dir\"`\n142:     Env        map[string]string `json:\"env\"`\n143: }\n144: \n145: type ExecuteResponse struct {\n146:     Stdout    string    `json:\"stdout\"`\n147:     Stderr    string    `json:\"stderr\"`\n148:     ExitCode  int       `json:\"exit_code\"`\n149:     Duration  float64   `json:\"duration\"`\n150:     StartTime time.Time `json:\"start_time\"`\n151:     EndTime   time.Time `json:\"end_time\"`\n152: }\n153: ```\n154: \n155: #### Files\n156: \n157: ```go\n158: type FileInfo struct {\n159:     Path     string    `json:\"path\"`\n160:     Size     int64     `json:\"size\"`\n161:     Mode     string    `json:\"mode\"`\n162:     Modified time.Time `json:\"modified\"`\n163: }\n164: \n165: type UploadFileRequest struct {\n166:     Path    string `json:\"path\" binding:\"required\"`\n167:     Content string `json:\"content\" binding:\"required\"`\n168:     Mode    string `json:\"mode\"`\n169: }\n170: \n171: type FileEntry struct {\n172:     Name     string    `json:\"name\"`\n173:     Size     int64     `json:\"size\"`\n174:     Modified time.Time `json:\"modified\"`\n175:     Mode     string    `json:\"mode\"`\n176:     IsDir    bool      `json:\"is_dir\"`\n177: }\n178: \n179: type ListFilesResponse struct {\n180:     Files []FileEntry `json:\"files\"`\n181: }\n182: ```\n183: \n184: ### 3.5 х╕╕щЗП\n185: \n186: | х╕╕щЗП | хА╝ | шп┤цШО |\n187: |------|-----|------|\n188: | `TimeoutExitCode` | `124` | ш╢ЕцЧ╢щААхЗ║чаБ |\n189: | `MaxBodySize` | `32 << 20` (32 MiB) | HTTP шп╖ц▒Вф╜Ухдзх░ПщЩРхИ╢ |\n190: | `PublicKeyEnvVar` | `\"PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY\"` | хЕмщТечОпхвГхПШщЗПхРН |\n191: | `maxFileMode` | `0777` | цЬАхдзцЦЗф╗╢цЭГщЩР |\n192: \n193: ---\n194: \n195: ## 4. API хРИч║ж\n196: \n197: ### 4.1 члпчВ╣хИЧшби\n198: \n199: | Method | Path | Middleware | Handler | Description |\n200: |--------|------|------------|---------|-------------|\n201: | POST | `/api/execute` | JWT | `ExecuteHandler` | цЙзшбМхС╜ф╗д |\n202: | POST | `/api/files` | JWT | `UploadFileHandler` | ф╕Кф╝ацЦЗф╗╢ |\n203: | GET | `/api/files` | JWT | `ListFilesHandler` | хИЧхЗ║цЦЗф╗╢ |\n204: | GET | `/api/files/*path` | JWT | `DownloadFileHandler` | ф╕Лш╜╜цЦЗф╗╢ |\n205: | GET | `/health` | none | `HealthCheckHandler` | хБех║╖цгАцЯе |\n206: \n207: ### 4.2 шп╖ц▒В/хУНх║Фца╝х╝П\n208: \n209: #### Execute\n210: \n211: ```json\n212: // POST /api/execute - Request\n213: {\n214:     \"command\": [\"ls\", \"-la\"],\n215:     \"timeout\": \"30s\",\n216:     \"working_dir\": \"/workspace\",\n217:     \"env\": {\"DEBUG\": \"true\"}\n218: }\n219: \n220: // Response - Success\n221: {\n222:     \"stdout\": \"total 4\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 02:14 .\\n\",\n223:     \"stderr\": \"\",\n224:     \"exit_code\": 0,\n225:     \"duration\": 0.023,\n226:     \"start_time\": \"2024-04-11T02:14:00Z\",\n227:     \"end_time\": \"2024-04-11T02:14:00Z\"\n228: }\n229: \n230: // Response - Error (timeout)\n231: {\n232:     \"stdout\": \"\",\n233:     \"stderr\": \"context deadline exceeded\",\n234:     \"exit_code\": 124,\n235:     \"duration\": 60.0,\n236:     \"start_time\": \"2024-04-11T02:14:00Z\",\n237:     \"end_time\": \"2024-04-11T02:15:00Z\"\n238: }\n239: ```\n240: \n241: #### Upload File\n242: \n243: ```json\n244: // POST /api/files - JSON Request\n245: {\n246:     \"path\": \"test.txt\",\n247:     \"content\": \"SGVsbG8gV29ybGQ=\",  // Base64 encoded\n248:     \"mode\": \"0644\"\n249: }\n250: \n251: // POST /api/files - Multipart Request\n252: // Content-Type: multipart/form-data\n253: // Form fields: path, file, mode (optional)\n254: \n255: // Response - Success\n256: {\n257:     \"path\": \"test.txt\",\n258:     \"size\": 11,\n259:     \"mode\": \"0644\",\n260:     \"modified\": \"2024-04-11T02:14:00Z\"\n261: }\n262: ```\n263: \n264: #### List Files\n265: \n266: ```json\n267: // GET /api/files?path=/workspace\n268: \n269: // Response\n270: {\n271:     \"files\": [\n272:         {\"name\": \"test.txt\", \"size\": 11, \"modified\": \"2024-04-11T02:14:00Z\", \"mode\": \"0644\", \"is_dir\": false},\n273:         {\"name\": \"subdir\", \"size\": 0, \"modified\": \"2024-04-11T02:14:00Z\", \"mode\": \"0755\", \"is_dir\": true}\n274:     ]\n275: }\n276: ```\n277: \n278: #### Health Check\n279: \n280: ```json\n281: // GET /health\n282: \n283: // Response\n284: {\n285:     \"status\": \"ok\",\n286:     \"service\": \"PicoD\",\n287:     \"version\": \"0.0.1\",\n288:     \"uptime\": \"1h2m3s\"\n289: }\n290: ```\n291: \n292: ### 4.3 щФЩшппхУНх║Ф\n293: \n294: | Status Code | Error Code | Description |\n295: |-------------|------------|-------------|\n296: | 400 | 400 | Bad Request (malformed JSON, missing fields) |\n297: | 401 | 401 | Unauthorized (missing/invalid JWT) |\n298: | 403 | 403 | Forbidden (path outside workspace) |\n299: | 404 | 404 | Not Found (file/directory not found) |\n300: | 500 | 500 | Internal Server Error |\n301: \n302: ```json\n303: // Generic error\n304: {\"error\": \"error message\", \"code\": 400}\n305: \n306: // Auth error\n307: {\"error\": \"Invalid token\", \"code\": 401, \"detail\": \"signature invalid\"}\n308: ```\n309: \n310: ---\n311: \n312: ## 5. хоЮчО░ч╗ЖшКВ\n313: \n314: ### 5.1 цЬНхКбхРпхКиц╡БчиЛ\n315: \n316: ```go\n317: func main() {\n318:     klog.InitFlags(nil)\n319:     flag.Parse()\n320:     \n321:     config := picod.Config{\n322:         Port:      *port,\n323:         Workspace: *workspace,\n324:     }\n325:     \n326:     server, err := picod.NewServer(config)\n327:     if err != nil {\n328:         klog.Fatalf(\"Failed to create server: %v\", err)\n329:     }\n330:     \n331:     if err := server.Run(); err != nil {\n332:         klog.Fatalf(\"Server error: %v\", err)\n333:     }\n334: }\n335: ```\n336: \n337: ### 5.2 Server хИЭхзЛхМЦ\n338: \n339: ```go\n340: func NewServer(config Config) (*Server, error) {\n341:     gin.SetMode(gin.ReleaseMode)\n342:     engine := gin.New()\n343:     engine.Use(gin.Logger(), gin.Recovery())\n344:     \n345:     authManager := &AuthManager{}\n346:     if err := authManager.LoadPublicKeyFromEnv(); err != nil {\n347:         klog.Fatalf(\"Failed to load public key: %v\", err)\n348:     }\n349:     \n350:     s := &Server{\n351:         engine:  engine,\n352:         config:  config,\n353:         authManager: authManager,\n354:         startTime: time.Now(),\n355:     }\n356:     \n357:     if err := s.setWorkspace(config.Workspace); err != nil {\n358:         return nil, err\n359:     }\n360:     \n361:     s.setupRoutes()\n362:     return s, nil\n363: }\n364: ```\n365: \n366: ### 5.3 ш╖пчФ▒шо╛ч╜о\n367: \n368: ```go\n369: func (s *Server) setupRoutes() {\n370:     api := s.engine.Group(\"/api\")\n371:     api.Use(s.authManager.AuthMiddleware())\n372:     {\n373:         api.POST(\"/execute\", s.ExecuteHandler)\n374:         api.POST(\"/files\", s.UploadFileHandler)\n375:         api.GET(\"/files\", s.ListFilesHandler)\n376:         api.GET(\"/files/*path\", s.DownloadFileHandler)\n377:     }\n378:     s.engine.GET(\"/health\", s.HealthCheckHandler)\n379: }\n380: ```\n381: \n382: ### 5.4 JWT шодшпБф╕нщЧ┤ф╗╢\n383: \n384: ```go\n385: func (am *AuthManager) AuthMiddleware() gin.HandlerFunc {\n386:     return func(c *gin.Context) {\n387:         authHeader := c.GetHeader(\"Authorization\")\n388:         if authHeader == \"\" {\n389:             c.JSON(http.StatusUnauthorized, gin.H{\n390:                 \"error\":  \"missing authorization header\",\n391:                 \"code\":   401,\n392:                 \"detail\": \"JWT required\",\n393:             })\n394:             c.Abort()\n395:             return\n396:         }\n397:         \n398:         parts := strings.Split(authHeader, \" \")\n399:         if len(parts) != 2 || parts[0] != \"Bearer\" {\n400:             c.JSON(http.StatusUnauthorized, gin.H{\n401:                 \"error\":  \"invalid authorization header format\",\n402:                 \"code\":   401,\n403:                 \"detail\": \"Use Bearer <token>\",\n404:             })\n405:             c.Abort()\n406:             return\n407:         }\n408:         \n409:         tokenString := parts[1]\n410:         token, err := jwt.Parse(tokenString, func(token *jwt.Token) (interface{}, error) {\n411:             if _, ok := token.Method.(*jwt.SigningMethodRSA); !ok {\n412:                 return nil, fmt.Errorf(\"unexpected signing method: %v\", token.Header[\"alg\"])\n413:             }\n414:             am.mu.RLock()\n415:             defer am.mu.RUnlock()\n416:             return am.publicKey, nil\n417:         }, jwt.WithExpirationRequired(), jwt.WithIssuedAt(), jwt.WithLeeway(time.Minute))\n418:         \n419:         if err != nil || !token.Valid {\n420:             c.JSON(http.StatusUnauthorized, gin.H{\n421:                 \"error\":  \"Invalid token\",\n422:                 \"code\":   401,\n423:                 \"detail\": err.Error(),\n424:             })\n425:             c.Abort()\n426:             return\n427:         }\n428:         \n429:         c.Request.Body = http.MaxBytesReader(c.Writer, c.Request.Body, MaxBodySize)\n430:         c.Next()\n431:     }\n432: }\n433: ```\n434: \n435: ### 5.5 хЕмщТехКаш╜╜\n436: \n437: ```go\n438: func (am *AuthManager) LoadPublicKeyFromEnv() error {\n439:     keyData := os.Getenv(PublicKeyEnvVar)\n440:     if keyData == \"\" {\n441:         return fmt.Errorf(\"environment variable %s is not set\", PublicKeyEnvVar)\n442:     }\n443:     \n444:     block, _ := pem.Decode([]byte(keyData))\n445:     if block == nil {\n446:         return fmt.Errorf(\"failed to decode PEM block\")\n447:     }\n448:     \n449:     pubKey, err := x509.ParsePKIXPublicKey(block.Bytes)\n450:     if err != nil {\n451:         return fmt.Errorf(\"failed to parse public key: %v\", err)\n452:     }\n453:     \n454:     rsaPubKey, ok := pubKey.(*rsa.PublicKey)\n455:     if !ok {\n456:         return fmt.Errorf(\"public key is not RSA\")\n457:     }\n458:     \n459:     am.mu.Lock()\n460:     defer am.mu.Unlock()\n461:     am.publicKey = rsaPubKey\n462:     \n463:     return nil\n464: }\n465: ```\n466: \n467: ### 5.6 хС╜ф╗дцЙзшбМ Handler\n468: \n469: ```go\n470: func (s *Server) ExecuteHandler(c *gin.Context) {\n471:     var req ExecuteRequest\n472:     if err := c.ShouldBindJSON(&req); err != nil {\n473:         c.JSON(http.StatusBadRequest, gin.H{\"error\": err.Error(), \"code\": 400})\n474:         return\n475:     }\n476:     \n477:     timeout := 60 * time.Second\n478:     if req.Timeout != \"\" {\n479:         var err error\n480:         timeout, err = time.ParseDuration(req.Timeout)\n481:         if err != nil {\n482:             c.JSON(http.StatusBadRequest, gin.H{\"error\": \"invalid timeout format\", \"code\": 400})\n483:             return\n484:         }\n485:     }\n486:     \n487:     ctx, cancel := context.WithTimeout(c.Request.Context(), timeout)\n488:     defer cancel()\n489:     \n490:     workingDir := s.workspaceDir\n491:     if req.WorkingDir != \"\" {\n492:         safePath, err := s.sanitizePath(req.WorkingDir)\n493:         if err != nil {\n494:             c.JSON(http.StatusForbidden, gin.H{\"error\": err.Error(), \"code\": 403})\n495:             return\n496:         }\n497:         workingDir = safePath\n498:     }\n499:     \n500:     cmd := exec.CommandContext(ctx, req.Command[0], req.Command[1:]...)\n501:     cmd.Dir = workingDir\n502:     \n503:     if req.Env != nil {\n504:         env := os.Environ()\n505:         for k, v := range req.Env {\n506:             env = append(env, k+\"=\"+v)\n507:         }\n508:         cmd.Env = env\n509:     }\n510:     \n511:     var stdout, stderr bytes.Buffer\n512:     cmd.Stdout = &stdout\n513:     cmd.Stderr = &stderr\n514:     \n515:     startTime := time.Now()\n516:     err := cmd.Run()\n517:     endTime := time.Now()\n518:     duration := endTime.Sub(startTime).Seconds()\n519:     \n520:     exitCode := 0\n521:     if ctx.Err() == context.DeadlineExceeded {\n522:         exitCode = TimeoutExitCode\n523:         stderr.WriteString(\"context deadline exceeded\\n\")\n524:     } else if err != nil {\n525:         exitCode = 1\n526:         if stderr.Len() > 0 {\n527:             stderr.WriteString(\"\\n\")\n528:         }\n529:         stderr.WriteString(err.Error())\n530:     } else if cmd.ProcessState != nil {\n531:         exitCode = cmd.ProcessState.ExitCode()\n532:     }\n533:     \n534:     c.JSON(http.StatusOK, ExecuteResponse{\n535:         Stdout:    stdout.String(),\n536:         Stderr:    stderr.String(),\n537:         ExitCode:  exitCode,\n538:         Duration:  duration,\n539:         StartTime: startTime,\n540:         EndTime:   endTime,\n541:     })\n542: }\n543: ```\n544: \n545: ### 5.7 ш╖пх╛ДхоЙхЕицгАцЯе\n546: \n547: ```go\n548: func (s *Server) sanitizePath(p string) (string, error) {\n549:     if s.workspaceDir == \"\" {\n550:         return \"\", fmt.Errorf(\"workspace directory not initialized\")\n551:     }\n552:     \n553:     resolvedWorkspace, err := filepath.EvalSymlinks(s.workspaceDir)\n554:     if err != nil {\n555:         resolvedWorkspace, _ = filepath.Abs(s.workspaceDir)\n556:         resolvedWorkspace = filepath.Clean(resolvedWorkspace)\n557:     }\n558:     \n559:     cleanPath := filepath.Clean(p)\n560:     if filepath.IsAbs(cleanPath) {\n561:         cleanPath = strings.TrimLeft(cleanPath, string(os.PathSeparator))\n562:     }\n563:     \n564:     fullPathCandidate := filepath.Clean(filepath.Join(resolvedWorkspace, cleanPath))\n565:     \n566:     relPath, relErr := filepath.Rel(resolvedWorkspace, fullPathCandidate)\n567:     if relErr != nil {\n568:         return \"\", fmt.Errorf(\"access denied\")\n569:     }\n570:     \n571:     if strings.HasPrefix(relPath, \"..\"+string(os.PathSeparator)) || relPath == \"..\" {\n572:         return \"\", fmt.Errorf(\"access denied\")\n573:     }\n574:     \n575:     resolvedFinalPath, err := filepath.EvalSymlinks(fullPathCandidate)\n576:     if err == nil {\n577:         if _, relErr := filepath.Rel(resolvedWorkspace, resolvedFinalPath); relErr != nil {\n578:             return \"\", fmt.Errorf(\"access denied\")\n579:         }\n580:         return resolvedFinalPath, nil\n581:     }\n582:     \n583:     return fullPathCandidate, nil\n584: }\n585: ```\n586: \n587: ### 5.8 цЦЗф╗╢ф╕Кф╝а Handler\n588: \n589: ```go\n590: func (s *Server) UploadFileHandler(c *gin.Context) {\n591:     contentType := c.ContentType()\n592:     \n593:     if strings.HasPrefix(contentType, \"multipart/form-data\") {\n594:         s.handleMultipartUpload(c)\n595:     } else {\n596:         s.handleJSONBase64Upload(c)\n597:     }\n598: }\n599: \n600: func (s *Server) handleJSONBase64Upload(c *gin.Context) {\n601:     var req UploadFileRequest\n602:     if err := c.ShouldBindJSON(&req); err != nil {\n603:         c.JSON(http.StatusBadRequest, gin.H{\"error\": err.Error(), \"code\": 400})\n604:         return\n605:     }\n606:     \n607:     content, err := base64.StdEncoding.DecodeString(req.Content)\n608:     if err != nil {\n609:         c.JSON(http.StatusBadRequest, gin.H{\"error\": \"invalid base64 content\", \"code\": 400})\n610:         return\n611:     }\n612:     \n613:     safePath, err := s.sanitizePath(req.Path)\n614:     if err != nil {\n615:         c.JSON(http.StatusForbidden, gin.H{\"error\": err.Error(), \"code\": 403})\n616:         return\n617:     }\n618:     \n619:     fileMode := parseFileMode(req.Mode)\n620:     if err := os.WriteFile(safePath, content, fileMode); err != nil {\n621:         c.JSON(http.StatusInternalServerError, gin.H{\"error\": err.Error(), \"code\": 500})\n622:         return\n623:     }\n624:     \n625:     c.JSON(http.StatusOK, FileInfo{\n626:         Path:     req.Path,\n627:         Size:     int64(len(content)),\n628:         Mode:     fmt.Sprintf(\"%o\", fileMode),\n629:         Modified: time.Now(),\n630:     })\n631: }\n632: ```\n633: \n634: ---\n635: \n636: ## 6. щФЩшппхдДчРЖ\n637: \n638: ### 6.1 щФЩшппч▒╗хЮЛ\n639: \n640: | щФЩшппхЬ║цЩп | HTTP чК╢цАБчаБ | щФЩшппф┐бцБп |\n641: |----------|-------------|----------|\n642: | ч╝║х░С Authorization Header | 401 | `missing authorization header` |\n643: | JWT ца╝х╝ПщФЩшпп | 401 | `invalid authorization header format` |\n644: | JWT цЧацХИ/ш┐ЗцЬЯ | 401 | `Invalid token` |\n645: | шп╖ц▒Вф╜Уш╢Еш┐ЗщЩРхИ╢ | 400 | `http: request body too large` |\n646: | ш╖пх╛Дф╕НхЬи Workspace хЖЕ | 403 | `access denied` |\n647: | цЦЗф╗╢цЬкцЙ╛хИ░ | 404 | `file not found` |\n648: | цЬНхКбхЩихЖЕщГищФЩшпп | 500 | щФЩшппцППш┐░ |\n649: \n650: ### 6.2 щФЩшппхдДчРЖчнЦчХе\n651: \n652: - цЙАцЬЙщФЩшппш┐ФхЫЮ JSON ца╝х╝П `{\"error\": string, \"code\": int}`\n653: - шодшпБщФЩшппщвЭхдЦхМЕхРл `detail` хнЧцо╡\n654: - ш╖пх╛ДхоЙхЕицгАцЯехд▒ш┤еш┐ФхЫЮ 403я╝Мф╕НщАПщЬ▓хЖЕщГиш╖пх╛Дч╗УцЮД\n655: - ш╢ЕцЧ╢ш┐ФхЫЮ exit code 124я╝Иф╕О `timeout` хС╜ф╗дф╕АшЗ┤я╝Й\n656: \n657: ---\n658: \n659: ## 7. ц╡ЛшпХчнЦчХе\n660: \n661: ### 7.1 хНХхЕГц╡ЛшпХ\n662: \n663: | цибхЭЧ | ц╡ЛшпХщЗНчВ╣ |\n664: |------|----------|\n665: | `AuthManager` | хЕмщТехКаш╜╜уАБToken щкМшпБуАБщФЩшппхдДчРЖ |\n666: | `ExecuteHandler` | хС╜ф╗дцЙзшбМуАБш╢ЕцЧ╢хдДчРЖуАБчОпхвГхПШщЗП |\n667: | `UploadFileHandler` | JSON ф╕Кф╝ауАБMultipart ф╕Кф╝ауАБш╖пх╛ДщкМшпБ |\n668: | `ListFilesHandler` | цЦЗф╗╢хИЧшбиуАБчЫох╜ХщБНхОЖ |\n669: | `DownloadFileHandler` | цЦЗф╗╢ф╕Лш╜╜уАБContent-Type |\n670: | `sanitizePath` | ш╖пх╛Дчй┐ш╢КщШ▓х╛буАБчмжхП╖щУ╛цОехдДчРЖ |\n671: \n672: ### 7.2 ц╡ЛшпХхЬ║цЩп\n673: \n674: | хЬ║цЩп | щвДцЬЯч╗УцЮЬ |\n675: |------|----------|\n676: | цЬЙцХИ JWT шп╖ц▒В | цЙзшбМцИРхКЯя╝Мш┐ФхЫЮч╗УцЮЬ |\n677: | ч╝║х░С JWT | 401 Unauthorized |\n678: | цЧацХИ JWT | 401 Unauthorized |\n679: | хС╜ф╗дш╢ЕцЧ╢ | exit_code = 124 |\n680: | ш╖пх╛Дчй┐ш╢Кх░ЭшпХ | 403 Forbidden |\n681: | цЦЗф╗╢ф╕Кф╝ацИРхКЯ | ш┐ФхЫЮцЦЗф╗╢ф┐бцБп |\n682: | ф╕НхнШхЬичЪДцЦЗф╗╢ф╕Лш╜╜ | 404 Not Found |\n683: \n684: ### 7.3 ц╡ЛшпХшжЖчЫЦчОЗчЫоцаЗ\n685: \n686: | ч╗Дф╗╢ | чЫоцаЗшжЖчЫЦчОЗ |\n687: |------|-----------|\n688: | auth.go | 90% |\n689: | execute.go | 90% |\n690: | files.go | 90% |\n691: \n692: ---\n693: \n694: ## 8. щЕНч╜о\n695: \n696: ### 8.1 CLI хПВцХ░\n697: \n698: | Flag | Type | Default | Description |\n699: |------|------|---------|-------------|\n700: | `-port` | int | 8080 | PicoD цЬНхКбхЩичЫСхРмчлпхПг |\n701: | `-workspace` | string | \"\" | цЦЗф╗╢цУНф╜Ьца╣чЫох╜Хя╝Ищ╗Шшодф╕║х╜УхЙНх╖еф╜ЬчЫох╜Хя╝Й |\n702: \n703: ### 8.2 чОпхвГхПШщЗП\n704: \n705: | Name | Required | Description |\n706: |------|----------|-------------|\n707: | `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` | Yes | PEM ч╝ЦчаБчЪД RSA хЕмщТе |\n708: \n709: ---\n710: \n711: ## 9. ф╛Эш╡Ц\n712: \n713: ### 9.1 хдЦщГиф╛Эш╡Ц\n714: \n715: | Package | Version | Purpose |\n716: |---------|---------|---------|\n717: | `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` | ^1.9.x | HTTP цбЖцЮ╢ |\n718: | `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` | ^5.0.0 | JWT щкМшпБ |\n719: | `k8s.io/klog/v2` | ^2.x | цЧех┐Ч |\n720: \n721: ### 9.2 хЖЕщГиф╛Эш╡Ц\n722: \n723: | Module | Purpose |\n724: |--------|---------|\n725: | цЧа | чЛмчлЛцибхЭЧя╝Мф╕Нф╛Эш╡ЦхЕ╢ф╗Ц agentcube хМЕ |\n726: \n727: ---\n728: \n729: ## 10. хПВшАГ\n730: \n731: - [Code Execution Design](code-execution/design.md)\n732: - [Deployment client-go](deployment/client-go.md)\n733: - [sdd_prompt.md](.sdd_prompt.md)\n\n(End of file - total 733 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-015 тАФ PicoD хС╜ф╗дцЙзшбМ API\n\n- **AR ID**: AR-015\n- **Module**: `pkg/picod`\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: M\n- **Status**: ST-1 Completed (design.md)\n- **Previous Stage**: AR-015 ST-1 completed\n\n## 1. цжВш┐░\n\nцЬмшо╛шобцЦЗцбгцППш┐░ PicoD хС╜ф╗дцЙзшбМ API чЪДцКАцЬпхоЮчО░ч╗ЖшКВуАВPicoD цШпф╕Аф╕кхЯ║ф║О HTTP чЪДхС╜ф╗дшбМцЙзшбМцЬНхКбя╝МцПРф╛ЫхоЙхЕичЪДхС╜ф╗дцЙзшбМуАБцЦЗф╗╢ф╕Кф╝аф╕Лш╜╜хКЯшГ╜я╝МцФпцМБ JWT шодшпБхТМ Workspace чЫох╜ХщЪФчж╗уАВ\n\n### 1.1 чЫоцаЗ\n\n- хоЮчО░хоЙхЕичЪДхС╜ф╗дшбМцЙзшбМ API\n- цПРф╛ЫцЦЗф╗╢ф╕Кф╝ауАБф╕Лш╜╜уАБхИЧшбихКЯшГ╜\n- хЯ║ф║О JWT чЪДшп╖ц▒ВшодшпБ\n- Workspace чЫох╜ХщЪФчж╗хТМш╖пх╛ДхоЙхЕицгАцЯе\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/picod/design.md"